    Highcharts themes

    hc_purple_theme.Rd

    These functions can be used to modify the theme of a highcharts plot.

    Usage

    hc_purple_theme(hc)

hc_samarqand_theme(hc)

hc_web_theme(hc)

    Arguments

    hc

    A highcharts object

    Value

    A highcharts object

    Examples

    highcharter::hchart(
  cars, "point",
  highcharter::hcaes(x = speed, y = dist)
) |>
  hc_purple_theme()
